      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; analyst training records serve as proxy control.",
      "rationale": "Formal use-error analysis not required at MRL 2. Analysts hold documented CFD competency certifications and simulation was peer-reviewed by a second qualified engineer."
