      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; turbulence model selection documented in simulation plan.",
      "rationale": "SST k-omega turbulence model selected based on published literature for rotating blood-contacting devices. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification deferred per MRL 2 scope."
