      "acceptanceCriteria": "All material properties and boundary condition inputs must have documented sources with stated uncertainty; sensitivity analysis performed for top-3 influential inputs.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and power-law index sourced from ISO 10993-compliant measurements with ±3% uncertainty. One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis confirms NIH insensitive to viscosity variation within uncertainty band."
