      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; dimensional matching confirmed qualitatively.",
      "rationale": "Reynolds number and flow coefficient matching between validation experiment and COU operating conditions confirmed qualitatively. Formal equivalency mapping not required at MRL 2."
