    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions in CPB applications. This model has been applied in clinical research to support device safety submissions; the assessment team finds the evidence package sufficient for the stated regulatory purpose.",
